Nebude. Dýchej.

252
00:17:19,522 --> 00:17:20,695
Posaďte se.

253
00:17:22,691 --> 00:17:23,765
<i>Jin Gyung Hee</i>

254
00:17:29,899 --> 00:17:30,975
Baek Joon Soo,

255
00:17:35,438 --> 00:17:38,675
